works well, meanwhile the Maven's
```scala
java -cp scala-compiler-2.10.0.jar:scala-reflect-2.10.0.jar:scala-library-2.10.0.jar scala.tools.nsc.Main -deprecation src/main/scala/cernoch/scalogic/package.scala
```

ends in the loop.
